      • GUEST_ACCOUNTS_IGNORE_PUBLICATION_TYPE_PREFIX_PROP

        static final java.lang.String GUEST_ACCOUNTS_IGNORE_PUBLICATION_TYPE_PREFIX_PROP
        A property prefix that allow other plugins to ignore Guest Account Rights Policy Filter on particular Publication types.
        The property syntax must be :
        • key : prefix + Publication type simple name
        • value : Publication type full qualified name

        Example of use:
        NewsletterPlugin's plugin.prop could declare the property:

         jcmsplugin.collaborativespace.guestaccounts-rpf.ignore-publication-type.NewsletterContent: generated.NewsletterContent
        ESNPlugin's plugin.prop could declare the properties:
         jcmsplugin.collaborativespace.guestaccounts-rpf.ignore-publication-type.MemberProfile: generated.MemberProfile
 jcmsplugin.collaborativespace.guestaccounts-rpf.ignore-publication-type.MemberCategories: generated.MemberCategories
        Since:
        csp-4.1
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values
